Name: contact support

description: the user will be able to send inquiry to the admin.

players: user

preconditions:
- the user have to be already registered and login.

Basic flow:
	1) login
	2) scroll down the screen
	3) press "contact us"
	4) fill your name and your email in the place desined for it.
  5) fill your messegein the place desined for it.
  6) press send.

alternate flow:
------
exception flow:
------

post conditions:
the messege will be sent to the admin.
